sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant AN as SOC Analyst
  participant FE as Next.js Frontend
  participant BE as FastAPI Backend
  participant CB as context_builder
  participant AI as ai_runner / LLM
  participant SP as safety_policy
  participant AX as ansible_exec
  participant SRV as Monitored Server
  participant FV as fix_verifier
  participant ES as Elasticsearch
  participant AR as archiver
  Note over BE,AI: Automated investigation (watcher)
  BE->>CB: build incident context (alerts, IOCs, host)
  CB->>AI: prompt (summary, narrative, risk, playbook)
  AI-->>BE: ai_summary + ai_risk + playbook_yaml
  BE->>SP: classify playbook safety tier
  SP-->>BE: tier + blocked_reasons
  BE-->>FE: investigation awaiting_approval
  AN->>FE: review summary + playbook
  AN->>BE: approve (X-ARIA-Admin-Secret)
  BE->>AX: execute approved playbook
  AX->>SRV: SSH run (evidence, containment, hardening)
  SRV-->>AX: stdout + exit_code
  AX-->>BE: PlaybookRun completed
  BE->>FV: verify fix
  FV->>ES: re-query for recurring alerts
  ES-->>FV: new_alerts_found
  FV-->>BE: likely_fixed | not_fixed
  BE->>AR: archive full context
  AR-->>FE: case archived
